{"type":"article_comment","id":238390,"parentType":"article","parentId":14213,"uid":16374,"contents":"瓦赫宁根大学这栋宿舍楼据说是因为离校园很近，以国际学生为主，还经常有不知道哪里来的未成年人在那里逛来逛去，也许就是他们做的。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/O8xRO5s.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O8xRO5s.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/O8xRO5s.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/izjG1Qu.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/izjG1Qu.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/izjG1Qu.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n这个行为本身确实是针对华人的，挺恶劣，但搞笑的是瓦大的90后学生们一边希望维权，一边当记者来了后又不愿意接受采访。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1HoY6OU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1HoY6OU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1HoY6OU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqcOSE3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqcOSE3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RqcOSE3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xYuLfTc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xYuLfTc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xYuLfTc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ob74C7N.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ob74C7N.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ob74C7N.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n在Facebook上瓦大的舆论全体支持抵制这样的行为，有人贴出了与刻字者留下的代号oss026相同的一个tiktok账号截图，据说此人是奈梅亨Nimegen市的一个无业游民（未核实）。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xr4milj.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xr4milj.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xr4milj.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n此外，警察表示注意到了这起事件并希望能着手调查，但需要有人正式提出报案要求，目前还没有收到。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/aeOaVfI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aeOaVfI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aeOaVfI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-10","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}